---
title: Incident Response Flow
author: Guy Schamp
---

@theme clean
@direction TB

#lane Customer
  #start Report Issue
  Provide Details
  #end Resolved

#lane Support Agent
  Triage Ticket
  #decision Severity?
    -> high: Escalate to Engineering
    -> low: Apply Known Fix

#lane Engineering
  Investigate Root Cause
  Deploy Fix

#lane System
  Run Automated Tests
  #decision Tests Pass?
    -> yes: Close Ticket
    -> no: Investigate Root Cause

// Cross-lane edges (explicit)
Provide Details -> Triage Ticket
Apply Known Fix -> Close Ticket
Escalate to Engineering -> Investigate Root Cause
Deploy Fix -> Run Automated Tests
Close Ticket -> Resolved
